# lulzx's Claude Code Plugins

A marketplace of Claude Code plugins by [@lulzx](https://github.com/lulzx).

## Install

```bash
/plugin marketplace add lulzx/claude-code
```

## Available Plugins

### ubrowser

**The fastest, cheapest browser automation for Claude.**

- 2.2x faster than alternatives
- 70% fewer tokens via batch execution and ultra-compact snapshots
- [Repository](https://github.com/lulzx/ubrowser)

```bash
/plugin add ubrowser@lulzx/claude-code
```
